OL,3,CMarcus Arduini Monzo guilty of
OL,4,Cmurdering Daniel Anjorin, 14, in sword
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,8,Fmurdering 14-year-old Daniel Anjorin
OL,9,Fduring an attack with a sword in
OL,10,FHainault, north-east London.
OL,12,FMarcus Arduini Monzo, 37, had gone
OL,13,Finto a cannabis-induced psychosis when
OL,14,Fhe killed the teenager with a samurai
OL,15,Fsword in April last year, the Old
OL,16,FBailey heard.
OL,18,FMonzo was also convicted of three
OL,19,Fcounts of attempted murder, wounding
OL,20,Fwith intent, aggravated burglary, and
OL,21,Fpossessing a bladed article.
