OL,7,FHe was cleared of one count of
OL,8,Fattempted murder in relation to the
OL,9,Fvictim Henry De Los Rios Polina, but
OL,10,Ffound guilty of the lesser offence of
OL,11,Fwounding with intent to cause grievous
OL,12,Fbodily harm.
OL,14,FMonzo, who showed no emotion as the
OL,15,Fverdicts were read out, previously
OL,16,Fadmitted having the samurai sword used
OL,17,Fto kill Daniel and a katana sword
OL,18,Ffound in his van.
