OL,7,FGiving evidence at his trial, he said
OL,8,Fhe had no memory of what happened and
OL,9,Fclaimed his mental state had
OL,10,Fdiminished his responsibility for the
OL,11,Fcrimes.
OL,13,FHowever, the prosecution argued that
OL,14,Fpsychosis brought on by self-induced
OL,15,Fintoxication was no defence for murder.
OL,17,FThe violence took place during a 20-
OL,18,Fminute spree in April 2024. Monzo
OL,19,Ftargeted members of the public and
OL,20,Fpolice officers.
