OL,7,FHe killed and skinned his pet cat
OL,8,FWizard before running amok in Hainault.
OL,10,FMonzo launched the series of attacks
OL,11,Fby driving his grey Ford Transit van
OL,12,Finto Donato Iwule, who was
OL,13,F"catapulted" into a nearby garden
OL,14,Fbefore the vehicle smashed into a
OL,15,Fconcrete pillar and fence.
