OL,7,FHe went on to hit Mr Iwule in the neck
OL,8,Fwith his sword before running away,
OL,9,Fthe court was told. Jurors then heard
OL,10,Fthat Monzo then virtually decapitated
OL,11,FDaniel, who was wearing headphones on
OL,12,Fhis way to school.
OL,14,FWitness Maria Olmos said Monzo dropped
OL,15,Fto his knees and held his hands up
OL,16,Fafter the fatal attack on the teenager.
