OL,7,FNext he entered a property and
OL,8,Fattacked a couple who were sleeping in
OL,9,Fan upstairs bedroom with their young
OL,10,Fdaughter nearby. Monzo demanded to
OL,11,Fknow if they "believe in God" before
OL,12,Fhe left the property.
OL,14,FInspector Molloy Campbell tried to
OL,15,Fdetain Monzo in a car park and
OL,16,Freceived a slash wound to his hand.
OL,17,FThe defendant then climbed on to the
OL,18,Froof of a garage before he was finally
OL,19,Fapprehended.
