OL,7,FAfter the jury's verdict, it can now
OL,8,Fbe revealed that Monzo's online
OL,9,Fbehaviour showed an eclectic interest
OL,10,Fin violence, conspiracy theories,
OL,11,FIncel and far-right extremism as well
OL,12,Fas controversial figures such as
OL,13,FAndrew Tate.
OL,15,FHe had liked posts on X praising Adolf
OL,16,FHitler, references to various
OL,17,Fantisemitic conspiracy theories and
OL,18,Fmisogynistic Incel material.
