OL,7,FIn a reference to one conspiracy,
OL,8,FMonzo posted: "I live in London. Here
OL,9,Feverybody will agree that the city is
OL,10,FGREY. And the reason is BECAUSE they
OL,11,Fspray the sky ALL DAY, EVERY DAY".
OL,13,FThe chemtrail conspiracy theory
OL,14,Fasserts that governments or other
OL,15,Fmalicious actors are engaged in a
OL,16,Fsecret programme to disseminate toxic
OL,17,Fchemicals into the atmosphere.
OL,19,FMonzo will be sentenced on Friday at
OL,20,Fthe Old Bailey.
